-- CGT Union Aims to Extend Marseille Strike to Oil Refineries, Figaro Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-05T04:37:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/cgt-union-aims-to-extend-marseille-strike-to-oil-refineries-figaro-says.html
The CGT union is seeking to extend a
strike that has blocked oil terminals at the port of Marseille
for a week to oil refineries, French daily Le Figaro reported,
citing regional CGT official Jean-Marie Michelucci.  Refinery strikes are likely to start before the end of this
week, according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  